description: After a hard-fought battle against Black Adam, Superman and Wonder Woman decide on a desperate tactic to ensure that he remains subdued. But Shazam (and his alter ego, Billy Batson) wonders if this is the right thing to do. How much longer will he remain loyal to Superman's campaign?
name: Chapter 19

description:
Brace yourselves, True Believers for a barrage of classic action and adventure starring Earth's mightiest heroes! First, the Avengers must do battle with the would-be tyrant Graviton. Next the maniacal super villain the Grim Reaper returns to confront his recently resurrected brother Wonder Man. Following a traitorous attack by Ant-Man, the team then find themselves in a desperate bid to save the Wasp from the deranged robot Ultron. Even more trouble is in store when Count Nefaria decides to target the Avengers once again. Finally, the team head into space for an intergalactic adventure with the Guardians of the Galaxy.

Collects Avengers (1963) #158-167.
name: The Avengers: The Bride Of Ultron

description:
This latest volume begins with Beast being tormented by the mysterious Manipulator, an empathic evildoer who takes over his very being! Then Black Panther clashes with The Stinger, whilst the other Avengers battle Bloodhawk, a mutant with an incredible tale to tell. Next, the team's active roster is restricted to just seven members by order of their government liaison Henry Gyrich, For those who make the cut, trouble's just around the corner courtesy of Crusher Creel AKA The Absorbing Man. Finally, Quicksilver and the Scarlet Witch's incredible origin comes back to haunt them, as the Scarlet Witch is taken over by the arcane evildoer, Chthon. Get ready for a barrage of classic Marvel action courtesy of the Earth's mightiest heroes!

Collects Avengers(1963) #178-187.
name: The Avengers: Nights Of Wundagore

description:
In the second issue of the new, digital-first series, the search for a missing holiday choir leads Batman and Nightwing into a confrontation with Mr. Freeze! But in this heartfelt Christmas tale, the frozen fiend’s motives aren’t as nefarious as they seem…

And on a festive New Year’s Eve, Catwoman thinks she’ll be spending a quiet night at home, contemplating her New Year’s resolutions—until Poison Ivy and Harley Quinn show up, that is!
name: Christmas; New Year's Eve

description:
A flawed demigod decides his destiny is to perfect the universe! It's too much power for one man, and it'll take over a dozen powerful men and women - Earth's Mightiest Heroes and the Guardians of the Galaxy - to stop him! Plus: The Avengers face additional endangerment from aliens, Atlanteans and automatons! Guest-starring Captain Marvel, Ms. Marvel, Doctor Strange and more!

Collects Avengers(1963) #168-177.
name: The Avengers: The Korvac Saga
